title: Plastic nurdles found at 84% of UK sites of special scientific interest
summary: Environmental charity Fidra reports that 168 out of 195 Sites of Special Scientific Interest (SSSIs) it surveyed are contaminated with small plastic pellets. The findings highlight significant concerns about pollution in protected areas. Fidra is calling for action to address this environmental issue.
